  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the white wine and cook until reduced by half.",
    "Add the fish stock and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cod fillets and cook for 2-3 minutes per side.",
    "Add the shichimi togarashi and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Stir in the cod roe (if using) and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Remove the pot from the heat and stir in the lemon juice and softened butter.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the bisque hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley (if desired)."
  ],
